{
  "video_id": "VQRjouwKDlU",
  "title": "4 reasons to learn a new language | John McWhorter",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12840.0,
      "end_time": 15416.0,
      "text": "The language I'm speaking right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15440.0,
      "end_time": 19776.0,
      "text": "is on its way to becoming the world's universal language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19800.0,
      "end_time": 22136.0,
      "text": "for better or for worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22160.0,
      "end_time": 23376.0,
      "text": "Let's face it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23400.0,
      "end_time": 25256.0,
      "text": "it's the language of the internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25280.0,
      "end_time": 27256.0,
      "text": "it's the language of finance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27280.0,
      "end_time": 29616.0,
      "text": "it's the language of air traffic control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29640.0,
      "end_time": 31160.0,
      "text": "of popular music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31400.0,
      "end_time": 32256.0,
      "text": "diplomacy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32280.0,
      "end_time": 33720.0,
      "text": "English is everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34320.0,
      "end_time": 38416.0,
      "text": "Now, Mandarin Chinese is spoken by more people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38440.0,
      "end_time": 40936.0,
      "text": "but more Chinese people are learning English"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40960.0,
      "end_time": 43656.0,
      "text": "than English speakers are learning Chinese."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43680.0,
      "end_time": 45416.0,
      "text": "Last I heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45440.0,
      "end_time": 48896.0,
      "text": "there are two dozen universities in China right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48920.0,
      "end_time": 51656.0,
      "text": "teaching all in English."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51680.0,
      "end_time": 53800.0,
      "text": "English is taking over."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53680.0,
      "end_time": 55376.0,
      "text": "And in addition to that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55400.0,
      "end_time": 58160.0,
      "text": "it's been predicted that at the end of the century"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58400.0,
      "end_time": 61160.0,
      "text": "almost all of the languages that exist now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61400.0,
      "end_time": 62296.0,
      "text": "there are about 6,000 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 62320.0,
      "end_time": 64215.0,
      "text": "will no longer be spoken."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64239.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66839.0,
      "text": "There will only be some hundreds left."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 67360.0,
      "end_time": 68976.0,
      "text": "And on top of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 69000.0,
      "end_time": 73576.0,
      "text": "it's at the point where instant translation of live speech"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73600.0,
      "end_time": 76720.0,
      "text": "is not only possible, but it gets better every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77360.0,
      "end_time": 80960.0,
      "text": "The reason I'm reciting those things to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80120.0,
      "end_time": 83256.0,
      "text": "is because I can tell that we're getting to the point"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83280.0,
      "end_time": 85496.0,
      "text": "where a question is going to start being asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85520.0,
      "end_time": 89560.0,
      "text": "which is: Why should we learn foreign languages --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89800.0,
      "end_time": 93560.0,
      "text": "other than if English happens to be foreign to one?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93800.0,
      "end_time": 96960.0,
      "text": "Why bother to learn another one when it's getting to the point"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96120.0,
      "end_time": 101600.0,
      "text": "where almost everybody in the world will be able to communicate in one?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102560.0,
      "end_time": 104376.0,
      "text": "I think there are a lot of reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104400.0,
      "end_time": 106736.0,
      "text": "but I first want to address"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106760.0,
      "end_time": 109616.0,
      "text": "the one that you're probably most likely to have heard of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109640.0,
      "end_time": 113976.0,
      "text": "because actually it's more dangerous than you might think."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114000.0,
      "end_time": 115736.0,
      "text": "And that is the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115760.0,
      "end_time": 118536.0,
      "text": "that a language channels your thoughts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118560.0,
      "end_time": 122936.0,
      "text": "that the vocabulary and the grammar of different languages"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 122960.0,
      "end_time": 126776.0,
      "text": "gives everybody a different kind of acid trip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 126800.0,
      "end_time": 128150.0,
      "text": "so to speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 128389.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132256.0,
      "text": "That is a marvelously enticing idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132280.0,
      "end_time": 133576.0,
      "text": "but it's kind of fraught."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 133600.0,
      "end_time": 137550.0,
      "text": "So it's not that it's untrue completely."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 137800.0,
      "end_time": 140895.0,
      "text": "So for example, in French and Spanish"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140919.0,
      "end_time": 145176.0,
      "text": "the word for table is, for some reason, marked as feminine."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145200.0,
      "end_time": 149136.0,
      "text": "So, \"la table,\" \"la mesa,\" you just have to deal with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149160.0,
      "end_time": 150656.0,
      "text": "It has been shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 150680.0,
      "end_time": 153760.0,
      "text": "that if you are a speaker of one of those languages"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153100.0,
      "end_time": 155775.0,
      "text": "and you happen to be asked"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 155800.0,
      "end_time": 159856.0,
      "text": "how you would imagine a table talking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159880.0,
      "end_time": 163775.0,
      "text": "then much more often than could possibly be an accident,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 163800.0,
      "end_time": 165496.0,
      "text": "a French or a Spanish speaker"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 165520.0,
      "end_time": 170376.0,
      "text": "says that the table would talk with a high and feminine voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 170400.0,
      "end_time": 174536.0,
      "text": "So if you're French or Spanish, to you, a table is kind of a girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 174560.0,
      "end_time": 177736.0,
      "text": "as opposed to if you are an English speaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 177760.0,
      "end_time": 179576.0,
      "text": "It's hard not to love data like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 179600.0,
      "end_time": 181736.0,
      "text": "and many people will tell you that that means"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 181760.0,
      "end_time": 186576.0,
      "text": "that there's a worldview that you have if you speak one of those languages."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 186600.0,
      "end_time": 187896.0,
      "text": "But you have to watch out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 187920.0,
      "end_time": 192375.0,
      "text": "because imagine if somebody put us under the microscope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 192400.0,
      "end_time": 194856.0,
      "text": "the us being those of us who speak English natively."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 194880.0,
      "end_time": 198736.0,
      "text": "What is the worldview from English?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 198760.0,
      "end_time": 201495.0,
      "text": "So for example, let's take an English speaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 201520.0,
      "end_time": 204816.0,
      "text": "Up on the screen, that is Bono."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 204840.0,
      "end_time": 206456.0,
      "text": "He speaks English."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 206480.0,
      "end_time": 209416.0,
      "text": "I presume he has a worldview."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 209440.0,
      "end_time": 213960.0,
      "text": "Now, that is Donald Trump."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 213120.0,
      "end_time": 214336.0,
      "text": "In his way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 214360.0,
      "end_time": 215776.0,
      "text": "he speaks English as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215800.0,
      "end_time": 217320.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 219520.0,
      "end_time": 222856.0,
      "text": "And here is Ms. Kardashian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222880.0,
      "end_time": 224856.0,
      "text": "and she is an English speaker, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 224880.0,
      "end_time": 227656.0,
      "text": "So here are three speakers of the English language."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 227680.0,
      "end_time": 231256.0,
      "text": "What worldview do those three people have in common?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 231280.0,
      "end_time": 236376.0,
      "text": "What worldview is shaped through the English language that unites them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 236400.0,
      "end_time": 238216.0,
      "text": "It's a highly fraught concept."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 238240.0,
      "end_time": 243960.0,
      "text": "And so gradual consensus is becoming that language can shape thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 243120.0,
      "end_time": 249576.0,
      "text": "but it tends to be in rather darling, obscure psychological flutters."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 249600.0,
      "end_time": 254200.0,
      "text": "It's not a matter of giving you a different pair of glasses on the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 254680.0,
      "end_time": 257160.0,
      "text": "Now, if that's the case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 257399.99999999997,
      "end_time": 258975.99999999997,
      "text": "then why learn languages?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 259000.0,
      "end_time": 261536.0,
      "text": "If it isn't going to change the way you think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 261560.0,
      "end_time": 263160.0,
      "text": "what would the other reasons be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 263720.0,
      "end_time": 264920.0,
      "text": "There are some."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 265600.0,
      "end_time": 270976.0,
      "text": "One of them is that if you want to imbibe a culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 271000.0,
      "end_time": 274136.0,
      "text": "if you want to drink it in, if you want to become part of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 274160.0,
      "end_time": 278560.0,
      "text": "then whether or not the language channels the culture --"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 278800.0,
      "end_time": 280150.0,
      "text": "and that seems doubtful --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 280400.0,
      "end_time": 281856.0,
      "text": "if you want to imbibe the culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 281880.0,
      "end_time": 284336.0,
      "text": "you have to control to some degree"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 284360.0,
      "end_time": 287696.0,
      "text": "the language that the culture happens to be conducted in."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 287720.0,
      "end_time": 289416.0,
      "text": "There's no other way."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 289440.0,
      "end_time": 291936.0,
      "text": "There's an interesting illustration of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 291960.0,
      "end_time": 295656.0,
      "text": "I have to go slightly obscure, but really you should seek it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 295680.0,
      "end_time": 300160.0,
      "text": "There's a movie by the Canadian film director Denys Arcand --"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 300400.0,
      "end_time": 302736.0,
      "text": "read out in English on the page, \"Dennis Ar-cand,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 302760.0,
      "end_time": 304960.0,
      "text": "if you want to look him up."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 304120.0,
      "end_time": 307176.0,
      "text": "He did a film called \"Jesus of Montreal.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 307200.0,
      "end_time": 309336.0,
      "text": "And many of the characters"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 309360.0,
      "end_time": 314416.0,
      "text": "are vibrant, funny, passionate, interesting French-Canadian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 314440.0,
      "end_time": 315776.0,
      "text": "French-speaking women."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 315800.0,
      "end_time": 318256.0,
      "text": "There's one scene closest to the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 318280.0,
      "end_time": 321736.0,
      "text": "where they have to take a friend to an Anglophone hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 321760.0,
      "end_time": 323856.0,
      "text": "In the hospital, they have to speak English."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 323880.0,
      "end_time": 326736.0,
      "text": "Now, they speak English but it's not their native language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 326760.0,
      "end_time": 328456.0,
      "text": "they'd rather not speak English."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 328480.0,
      "end_time": 330416.0,
      "text": "And they speak it more slowly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 330440.0,
      "end_time": 332416.0,
      "text": "they have accents, they're not idiomatic."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 332440.0,
      "end_time": 335136.0,
      "text": "Suddenly these characters that you've fallen in love with"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 335160.0,
      "end_time": 338560.0,
      "text": "become husks of themselves, they're shadows of themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 339280.0,
      "end_time": 340976.0,
      "text": "To go into a culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 341000.0,
      "end_time": 345160.0,
      "text": "and to only ever process people through that kind of skrim curtain"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 345400.0,
      "end_time": 347936.0,
      "text": "is to never truly get the culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 347960.0,
      "end_time": 350736.0,
      "text": "And so to the extent that hundreds of languages will be left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 350760.0,
      "end_time": 352150.0,
      "text": "one reason to learn them"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 352400.0,
      "end_time": 355736.0,
      "text": "is because they are tickets to being able to participate"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 355760.0,
      "end_time": 358150.0,
      "text": "in the culture of the people who speak them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 358400.0,
      "end_time": 361216.0,
      "text": "just by virtue of the fact that it is their code."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 361240.0,
      "end_time": 362480.0,
      "text": "So that's one reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 363440.0,
      "end_time": 364736.0,
      "text": "Second reason:"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 364760.0,
      "end_time": 366176.0,
      "text": "it's been shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 366200.0,
      "end_time": 371135.0,
      "text": "that if you speak two languages, dementia is less likely to set in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 371160.0,
      "end_time": 374496.0,
      "text": "and that you are probably a better multitasker."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 374520.0,
      "end_time": 377936.0,
      "text": "And these are factors that set in early,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 377960.0,
      "end_time": 379895.0,
      "text": "and so that ought to give you some sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 379920.0,
      "end_time": 384456.0,
      "text": "of when to give junior or juniorette lessons in another language."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 384480.0,
      "end_time": 386896.0,
      "text": "Bilingualism is healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 386920.0,
      "end_time": 388816.0,
      "text": "And then, third --"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 388840.0,
      "end_time": 392239.0,
      "text": "languages are just an awful lot of fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 392800.0,
      "end_time": 394536.0,
      "text": "Much more fun than we're often told."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 394560.0,
      "end_time": 397856.0,
      "text": "So for example, Arabic: \"kataba,\" he wrote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 397880.0,
      "end_time": 401960.0,
      "text": "\"yaktubu,\" he writes, she writes."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 401120.0,
      "end_time": 404136.0,
      "text": "\"Uktub,\" write, in the imperative."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 404160.0,
      "end_time": 406560.0,
      "text": "What do those things have in common?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 406800.0,
      "end_time": 408176.0,
      "text": "All those things have in common"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 408200.0,
      "end_time": 411736.0,
      "text": "the consonants sitting in the middle like pillars."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 411760.0,
      "end_time": 413216.0,
      "text": "They stay still,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 413240.0,
      "end_time": 416376.0,
      "text": "and the vowels dance around the consonants."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 416400.0,
      "end_time": 419575.0,
      "text": "Who wouldn't want to roll that around in their mouths?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 419600.0,
      "end_time": 421160.0,
      "text": "You can get that from Hebrew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 421400.0,
      "end_time": 424696.0,
      "text": "you can get that from Ethiopia's main language, Amharic."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 424720.0,
      "end_time": 426136.0,
      "text": "That's fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 426160.0,
      "end_time": 429576.0,
      "text": "Or languages have different word orders."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 429600.0,
      "end_time": 431816.0,
      "text": "Learning how to speak with different word order"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 431840.0,
      "end_time": 436816.0,
      "text": "is like driving on the different side of a street if you go to certain country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 436840.0,
      "end_time": 441335.0,
      "text": "or the feeling that you get when you put Witch Hazel around your eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 441360.0,
      "end_time": 442696.0,
      "text": "and you feel the tingle."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 442720.0,
      "end_time": 445296.0,
      "text": "A language can do that to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 445320.0,
      "end_time": 446536.0,
      "text": "So for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 446560.0,
      "end_time": 448576.0,
      "text": "\"The Cat in the Hat Comes Back,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 448600.0,
      "end_time": 451960.0,
      "text": "a book that I'm sure we all often return to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 451120.0,
      "end_time": 452376.0,
      "text": "like \"Moby Dick.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 452400.0,
      "end_time": 457496.0,
      "text": "One phrase in it is, \"Do you know where I found him?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 457520.0,
      "end_time": 460176.0,
      "text": "Do you know where he was? He was eating cake in the tub,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 460200.0,
      "end_time": 461416.0,
      "text": "Yes he was!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 461440.0,
      "end_time": 463776.0,
      "text": "Fine. Now, if you learn that in Mandarin Chinese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 463800.0,
      "end_time": 465560.0,
      "text": "then you have to master,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 465800.0,
      "end_time": 467335.0,
      "text": "\"You can know, I did where him find?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 467360.0,
      "end_time": 469176.0,
      "text": "He was tub inside gorging cake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 469200.0,
      "end_time": 471150.0,
      "text": "No mistake gorging chewing!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 471400.0,
      "end_time": 472256.0,
      "text": "That just feels good."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 472280.0,
      "end_time": 476575.0,
      "text": "Imagine being able to do that for years and years at a time."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 476600.0,
      "end_time": 480936.0,
      "text": "Or, have you ever learned any Cambodian?"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 480960.0,
      "end_time": 483976.0,
      "text": "Me either, but if I did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 484000.0,
      "end_time": 488616.0,
      "text": "I would get to roll around in my mouth not some baker's dozen of vowels"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 488640.0,
      "end_time": 489895.0,
      "text": "like English has,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 489920.0,
      "end_time": 492936.0,
      "text": "but a good 30 different vowels"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 492960.0,
      "end_time": 496856.0,
      "text": "scooching and oozing around in the Cambodian mouth"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 496880.0,
      "end_time": 499216.0,
      "text": "like bees in a hive."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 499240.0,
      "end_time": 501760.0,
      "text": "That is what a language can get you."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 502440.0,
      "end_time": 503695.0,
      "text": "And more to the point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 503720.0,
      "end_time": 507656.0,
      "text": "we live in an era when it's never been easier to teach yourself another language."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 507680.0,
      "end_time": 509936.0,
      "text": "It used to be that you had to go to a classroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 509960.0,
      "end_time": 512150.0,
      "text": "and there would be some diligent teacher --"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 512390.0,
      "end_time": 513655.0,
      "text": "some genius teacher in there --"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 513679.0,
      "end_time": 516150.0,
      "text": "but that person was only in there at certain times"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 516390.0,
      "end_time": 517295.0,
      "text": "and you had to go then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 517320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519136.00000000006,
      "text": "and then was not most times."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 519159.0,
      "end_time": 520559.0,
      "text": "You had to go to class."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 520974.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523736.00000000006,
      "text": "If you didn't have that, you had something called a record."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 523760.0,
      "end_time": 525456.0,
      "text": "I cut my teeth on those."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 525480.0,
      "end_time": 528176.0,
      "text": "There was only so much data on a record,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 528200.0,
      "end_time": 529456.0,
      "text": "or a cassette,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 529480.0,
      "end_time": 531816.0,
      "text": "or even that antique object known as a CD."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 531840.0,
      "end_time": 534456.0,
      "text": "Other than that you had books that didn't work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 534480.0,
      "end_time": 535856.0,
      "text": "that's just the way it was."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 535880.0,
      "end_time": 538776.0,
      "text": "Today you can lay down --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 538800.0,
      "end_time": 541256.0,
      "text": "lie on your living room floor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 541280.0,
      "end_time": 542496.0,
      "text": "sipping bourbon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 542520.0,
      "end_time": 545295.0,
      "text": "and teach yourself any language that you want to"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 545320.0,
      "end_time": 547896.0,
      "text": "with wonderful sets such as Rosetta Stone."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 547920.0,
      "end_time": 551550.0,
      "text": "I highly recommend the lesser known Glossika as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 551800.0,
      "end_time": 552376.0,
      "text": "You can do it any time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 552400.0,
      "end_time": 555000.0,
      "text": "therefore you can do it more and better."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 555480.0,
      "end_time": 559296.0,
      "text": "You can give yourself your morning pleasures in various languages."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 559320.0,
      "end_time": 563560.0,
      "text": "I take some \"Dilbert\" in various languages every single morning;"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 563800.0,
      "end_time": 564736.0,
      "text": "it can increase your skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 564760.0,
      "end_time": 566616.0,
      "text": "Couldn't have done it 20 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 566640.0,
      "end_time": 570175.0,
      "text": "when the idea of having any language you wanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 570200.0,
      "end_time": 571776.0,
      "text": "in your pocket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 571800.0,
      "end_time": 573295.0,
      "text": "coming from your phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 573320.0,
      "end_time": 577400.0,
      "text": "would have sounded like science fiction to very sophisticated people."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 577800.0,
      "end_time": 580335.0,
      "text": "So I highly recommend"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 580360.0,
      "end_time": 584336.0,
      "text": "that you teach yourself languages other than the one that I'm speaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 584360.0,
      "end_time": 587536.0,
      "text": "because there's never been a better time to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 587560.0,
      "end_time": 589550.0,
      "text": "It's an awful lot of fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 589800.0,
      "end_time": 590896.0,
      "text": "It won't change your mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 590920.0,
      "end_time": 594960.0,
      "text": "but it will most certainly blow your mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 594120.0,
      "end_time": 595336.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 595360.0,
      "end_time": 600161.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}